sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.cdbg

Interface CDebugInfoDataBase

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicCDebugInfoDataBase

    public interface CDebugInfoDataBase
    Database for C and C++ debug information. This is being kept as minimal as possible for now. It is not complete; for example, it will have to be extended to support scoped information (module scope, namespace scope).
